Marui Sold Beef From Contaminated Cattle at One Tokyo Store

-- B y   G e a r o i d   R e i d y
-- 
2011-07-19T03:31:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/marui-sold-beef-from-contaminated-cattle-at-one-tokyo-store-1-.html
Marui Group Co. said beef from
cattle contaminated by radiation was sold at one its stores in
 Tokyo .  A total of 13.2 kilograms (29 pounds) of the beef was put
on sale between June 12 and 14 at a store in Tokyo’s Kita-Senju,
according to a statement on Marui’s website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gearoid Reidy at 
 greidy1@bloomberg.net  